descriptionHtml:
Maid dress and headpiece, give it to Lydia or roleplay the lusty Arginian maid.
An clean and pretty lore friendly mod for once. 

Headpiece is for all races and genders, dress is female only :o)
Dress is craftable under mish and headpiece as jewelry 

Dress is based on Hentai\'s Vidala\'s dress, but uses an seperate mesh and texture.
